snippet.title: Backrooms Lost-Have a nice trip!
snippet.description:
#TuJiGaming#Backroomslost#
Today we are proud to announce that Backroom Lost has been launched on STEAM!
  With a team of three and a year of development and design, we have continued to troubleshoot game bugs, fix gameplay issues raised by players, add single-player and multiplayer modes to the game, and design different styles of layer styles with references to the original tiers. Moreover, horror elements and reveal elements are added to the game, to provide players with a different atmosphere within the backroom experience.
  HAVE A GOOD DAY IN THE BACKROOMS!

▼HOW can I get this game?
STEAM→store.steampowered.com/app/2924300/BackRoomsLost

▼I want to feedback some issues/I want to join this trip!
Discord→discord.gg/jevkg8T5Xq
Twitch→twitch.tv/backrooms_lost/videos
